profile:
Cornerstone Drafting and Design was founded in 1994 to serve the residential housing design needs of Durham Region and the G.T.A.

Darryl Kennedy  M.A.A.T.O.   B.C.Q.  , founder and president, is a graduate of Humber College’s Architectural Technology Co-op Program.

Darryl has been involved in various capacities of the residential construction industry since 1986.

Believing that keeping current on today’s evolving methods and technologies, Darryl continues to make education a solid element of his business practice, taking courses and seminars towards his continuing professional development.
name: Cornerstone Drafting And Design

profile:
J.Isles Architectural Services is a father & son team.

Justin designed and created the working drawings of his first custom home in his second year of college. After finishing at the top of his class, he worked for one of the premier residential design firms in Toronto. From there he has been involved with a variety of home builders and developers in all facets of the residential construction industry. This experience allows a unique perspective on how good design can simplify construction while also reducing costs.

Jon is a computer wizard and an AutoCAD expert who brings his own fresh and creative design flair to all our projects.

Together we can bring you ideas to life!
